ved. This is\nthe one friend indeed for it is a friend in need.\nIt aids him and does not take away his self-respect.\nThis bank is the house of your best friend.\nThe First National Bank\nof Montpelier\nEstablished l-;\nMember Federal Retire System\nVermont Mutual\nFire Insurance Company\nof Montpelier, Vt\nNINETY-THIRD YEAR\nCash Assets $260.833.00\nInsurance in Force $119,521,431.00\nPolicies written under Mutual or Taid-Up rian at\nactual cost no profit\nConsider this fact when placing your Automobile\nFire Insurance\nIf you are seeking Insurance! see our Local Agent\nMcAllister Kent\nAgents for Barre, Berlin and Orange\nA. W. Badger Co.\nA NEW AND CP-TO-D VTE AUTO AMBULANCB","height":"28528","width":"22092"}}
